Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.39,0:02:52.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the pirates who are \Nafter the One Piece...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.69,0:02:57.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...head for the New World, the \Nsecond half of the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.03,0:03:03.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, no one has ever fully explored it
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.28,0:03:06.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,except for Gold Roger, King of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.41,0:03:13.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The New World has ruined many \Npirates' dreams and ambitions.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.46,0:03:16.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Monkey D. Luffy,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.21,0:03:20.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a boy whose body turned to rubber \Nafter he ate the Gum-Gum Fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.66,0:03:22.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and his friends venture into that sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.05,0:03:26.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna become the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.23,0:03:31.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After landing on Punk Hazard;
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.82,0:03:34.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,an island with two parts, one \Nburning, the other frozen,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.15,0:03:37.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Straw Hats learned about \Nthe hideous experiments
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.57,0:03:40.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,performed by Caesar Clown, the Master,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.34,0:03:42.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and headed off to investigate.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.86,0:03:43.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.07,0:03:45.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An alliance?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.45,0:03:47.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a plan...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.16,0:03:50.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...to bring down one of the Four Emperors!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.00,0:03:58.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Formed! Luffy and Law's Pirate Alliance!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.68,0:04:09.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An alliance?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.39,0:04:15.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying that if we work together, \Nwe can take down an Emperor?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.23,0:04:16.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How absurd!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.86,0:04:22.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what he wants but don't \Nlisten to this jerk's fast-talk, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.70,0:04:30.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not saying we can beat \Nthe Emperor straight away.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.00,0:04:36.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All I'm saying is we'd get a chance \Nif we advance the plan step by step.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.08,0:04:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you say, Straw Hat-ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.84,0:04:44.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which of the Four Emperors \Nare you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.93,0:04:47.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Luffy, why are you interested?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.10,0:04:50.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't trust this guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.52,0:05:00.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Emperor's name is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.43,0:05:29.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.43,0:05:34.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.56,0:05:35.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.74,0:05:38.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.86,0:05:47.32,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,THE STRAW HATS' ENCAMPMENT
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.69,0:05:47.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.61,0:05:52.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna form an alliance \Nwith the Heart Pirates?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.28,0:05:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just went out to reclaim Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.50,0:05:58.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So how did you come back with \Nsuch an eccentric idea?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.92,0:06:00.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.01,0:06:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we ally ourselves with this \Ncreep who gives me the chills,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.50,0:06:06.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't be able to sleep in peace at night!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.06,0:06:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See, Luffy? Everybody's against it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.90,0:06:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's not do it. It's too risky.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.06,0:06:15.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We wanna travel at our own pace.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.40,0:06:16.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's right, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.71,0:06:20.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, it's too early to even \Nthink about the Four Emperors!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.58,0:06:22.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't fight them yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.65,0:06:25.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, treat this racoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.03,0:06:27.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget about some racoon now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.62,0:06:28.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.52,0:06:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.14,0:06:31.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.81,0:06:35.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Z-Zuber...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.73,0:06:41.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?! My body!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.24,0:06:44.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.93,0:06:47.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna go along with your decision
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.29,0:06:52.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but alliances between pirates \Nare often marked by betrayal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.77,0:06:55.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it's dangerous for you \Nsince you are so trusting.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.39,0:06:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Are you gonna betray me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.50,0:06:59.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.96,0:07:02.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, have at least a little doubt!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.28,0:07:06.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyhow, a pirate alliance \Nsounds like fun, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.32,0:07:10.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think Tra-guy is a good man but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.45,0:07:13.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...even if he isn't, don't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.91,0:07:17.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I have you guys who spent \Nthe last two years training!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.18,0:07:20.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.62,0:07:22.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy, you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.79,0:07:27.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't mention it! Luffy, \Nyou're making me blush!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.88,0:07:31.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I know we're zuper dependable but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.18,0:07:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We just do what we got to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.80,0:07:38.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not flattering me, you fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.19,0:07:43.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Alright, Luffy! You can count on us!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.44,0:07:47.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Zoro and the others wimp \Nout, I'll convince them!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.11,0:07:48.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.66,0:07:58.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Room.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.66,0:08:01.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shambles.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.80,0:08:13.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got it back! My great body!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.47,0:08:16.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew I liked myself the best when I'm me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.10,0:08:18.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Super!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.77,0:08:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm happy for you, Franky!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.94,0:08:26.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't ever take Chopper's body again. Ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.86,0:08:29.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.86,0:08:31.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...back to myself, too, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.31,0:08:34.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are there cuts and \Nbruises all over my body?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.76,0:08:37.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you guys do to it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.74,0:08:42.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I'm sorry. It's his fault.\N--I'm sorry. It's his fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.20,0:08:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?! You went out of \Ncontrol in Chopper's body
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.00,0:08:47.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I had no choice but to stop you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.95,0:08:50.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you didn't have to use \Nthe same technique you used
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.86,0:08:52.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to beat the Kraken!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.21,0:08:53.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I blame both of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.14,0:08:55.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I'm sorry!\N--I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.71,0:08:58.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should be happy just being \Nback to yourself, Chopper.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.37,0:09:02.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I have to be in \Nsomeone else's body again?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.52,0:09:05.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First, it was Franky and now, Sanji-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.48,0:09:08.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami became Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.36,0:09:13.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're looking good!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.46,0:09:17.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It wouldn't be funny if it happened to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.82,0:09:19.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.83,0:09:21.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chopper and Franky could
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.49,0:09:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,go back to themselves because \Ntheir bodies were here
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.20,0:09:29.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but since Sanji went out looking \Nfor the samurai in Nami's body,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.25,0:09:33.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you have no choice but take Sanji's body.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.52,0:09:35.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you do something about it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.03,0:09:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do anything without your body here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.62,0:09:44.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These are the children?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.01,0:09:46.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I wanna help them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.35,0:09:59.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm giving them this drug candy everyday.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.65,0:10:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're such a pain - just forget about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.84,0:10:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard they're drugged.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.70,0:10:07.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We know! Because I tested them!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.27,0:10:11.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just wanna take them home
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.47,0:10:14.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but it'll take a while for them to recover
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.17,0:10:16.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and most importantly, they are so big.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.07,0:10:20.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boy, I can't believe somebody's \Ndoing such a horrendous experiment.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.22,0:10:25.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turning people into giants is a \Nproject that has been underway for
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.80,0:10:27.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,hundreds of years by the World Government.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.22,0:10:33.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Government? For what purpose?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.08,0:10:35.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Military might, probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.81,0:10:38.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If they can produce an infinite \Namount of giant soldiers,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.88,0:10:40.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they'll become invincible.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.03,0:10:45.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Caesar wants to achieve the goal first
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.08,0:10:49.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and outsmart the Government and Vegapunk
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.56,0:10:51.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I don't think it's that easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.56,0:10:57.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really wanna help them?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.72,0:11:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't even know who they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.30,0:11:03.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I do. Although I don't know them well,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.87,0:11:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they asked me to help \Nwith tears in their eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.71,0:11:12.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like the Master tricked \Nthem and brought them here
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.59,0:11:17.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but they already know there is \Nsomething wrong with this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.66,0:11:27.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until I know that they are safe, \NI won't leave this island!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.13,0:11:30.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you willing to stay here alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.19,0:11:33.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not gonna leave my friend behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.65,0:11:36.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's what Nami and \NChopper want, I want it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.78,0:11:40.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Sanji wants to stick the \Nsamurai's body together.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.97,0:11:44.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You got to help us if you \Nwanna team up with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.28,0:11:50.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought so. You have no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.44,0:11:53.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think an alliance is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.95,0:12:00.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...a cooperative relationship just \Nfor some common goal, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.51,0:12:01.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.83,0:12:06.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen. Luffy's idea of an alliance \Nis a little different from yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.74,0:12:08.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like being friends, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.35,0:12:12.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're thinking of taking control, \Nit won't be that easy, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.53,0:12:14.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what they say.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.06,0:12:17.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once he feels sure about \Nsomething, he won't back down.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.59,0:12:19.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a pain in the ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.55,0:12:23.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His selfishness is as formidable \Nas the Four Emperors.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.10,0:12:24.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That must be hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.18,0:12:30.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what your friends want has \Nnothing to do with us at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.10,0:12:34.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Don't throw your booger at me, fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.69,0:12:36.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.40,0:12:39.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't move right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.73,0:12:40.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.19,0:12:45.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I understand. There is not much time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.41,0:12:48.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys have to take care of the samurai.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.08,0:12:52.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll look into the drug \Nthat the kids were taking.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.87,0:12:54.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is your ship's doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.37,0:12:58.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's got to come with me and help \Nme research it behind Caesar's back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.13,0:13:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, this is good.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.46,0:13:07.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry but I can't walk \Nright now so, thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.18,0:13:14.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't drop him, Tra-guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.46,0:13:17.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry! I shouldn't laugh! But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.90,0:13:19.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Super cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.86,0:13:22.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck, Chopper.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.57,0:13:23.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Count on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.49,0:13:30.95,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,THE BURNING LANDS
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.95,0:13:33.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,1, 2, 3!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.17,0:13:38.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,1, 2, 3!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.84,0:13:51.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, it's unlocked!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.73,0:13:53.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,1, 2, 3!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.02,0:14:04.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do they keep in this warehouse?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.58,0:14:17.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.03,0:14:23.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't see. It's too dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.76,0:14:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.81,0:15:27.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you mad?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.90,0:15:37.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As you can tell from the assassins earlier,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.14,0:15:43.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Caesar-ya wants to get rid of you \Nguys and White Chase-ya's G-5
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.71,0:15:45.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and take back those children.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.21,0:15:51.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until he gets what he wants, \Nhe won't stop attacking.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.21,0:15:55.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is a former Government scientist,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.44,0:15:57.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who became a criminal four years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.04,0:16:02.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the fact somebody is here on \Nthis restricted island leaks out,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.59,0:16:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he will lose this perfect hiding place.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.16,0:16:08.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why he'll try to \Nkill you all at any cost.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.53,0:16:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A 300 million berry bounty.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.14,0:16:15.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Logia-type Gas-Gas Fruit eater who owns
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.44,0:16:17.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,weapons of mass destruction.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.61,0:16:20.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's who Caesar Clown is.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.64,0:16:24.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,300 million?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.92,0:16:27.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those of you who can't use \NHaki, stay away from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.90,0:16:29.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not just a scientist.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.18,0:16:34.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those who can use Haki among \Nus are me and Zoro and Sanji.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.41,0:16:35.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.94,0:16:37.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think that's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.47,0:16:40.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna go back to the lab now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.62,0:16:45.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what we're gonna do is \Nkidnap the Master, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.33,0:16:46.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.89,0:16:50.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But why should we kidnap him?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.31,0:16:54.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Money? I thought the \NMaster guy is their boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.68,0:16:57.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who else can pay us a ransom?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.43,0:17:00.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not gonna do it for \Nmoney. Just to raise havoc.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.91,0:17:04.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Havoc?\N--What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.89,0:17:07.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no point to tell you
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.09,0:17:09.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,what lies ahead before we \Neven kidnap him successfully.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.24,0:17:13.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Focus on capturing Caesar Clown for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.20,0:17:15.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not gonna be easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.93,0:17:17.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh. Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.57,0:17:22.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you all the details \Nof my plan after that. However,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.34,0:17:25.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when we kidnap Caesar successfully,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.66,0:17:29.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,things will start moving \Nwhether you like it or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.09,0:17:32.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There will be no turning back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.65,0:17:39.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the last chance \Nfor you to reconsider.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.44,0:17:41.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's okay. We're with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.27,0:17:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, I will go along with \Nwhat you guys want to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.59,0:17:49.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You need to convince the rest of your crew.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.42,0:17:51.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.01,0:17:57.93,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,CAESAR CLOWN'S LABORATORY - THE FRONT
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.05,0:18:01.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard! Damn you creature!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.77,0:18:07.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Rebar" Smoothie!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.48,0:18:10.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fen Bock of the Gourd!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.90,0:18:16.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Rope-Tugging" Chappe!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.84,0:18:21.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Smoker-san! They are former \Nprisoners as we thought!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.96,0:18:23.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just looking a little different.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.77,0:18:31.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.57,0:18:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why did they say none of the \Nprisoners survived four years ago?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.15,0:18:47.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Smo-san, what are those people?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.91,0:18:50.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How should I know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.35,0:18:53.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, just hold them back!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.59,0:18:58.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to put the ship to sea...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.65,0:19:01.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...to make a report!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.09,0:19:04.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot! Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.18,0:19:15.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ring, ring, ring... Ring, ring, ring...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.37,0:19:17.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master, the Transponder Snail is ringing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.15,0:19:21.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.12,0:19:23.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They probably want to report \Nthey opened the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.83,0:19:27.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"And something came out."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.24,0:19:31.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"It attacked our comrades. Help us."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.52,0:19:34.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll just go on like that. Quite annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.25,0:19:39.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't often have this many visitors here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.67,0:19:42.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can stop gathering test subjects now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.96,0:19:43.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.09,0:19:57.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?! Master?! Hello?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.23,0:20:00.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please come in!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.70,0:20:05.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're in the Burning Lands! We \Nopened the door as you said!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.88,0:20:11.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No good! The Master is not picking up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.91,0:20:14.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's coming! What is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.57,0:20:17.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It came out of the building!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.61,0:20:20.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It killed all of our comrades! Just run!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.44,0:20:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Wh-Which way?!\N--Th-This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.12,0:21:09.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that thing?! It's \Nbigger than a mountain!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.53,0:21:38.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's coming! Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.29,0:21:41.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.16,0:21:58.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me tell you about my pet.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.24,0:22:03.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a very rare slime-type creature.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.06,0:22:08.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.59,0:22:11.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.10,0:22:15.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...can leave this island!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.52,0:22:30.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How does it feel to be loose after so long,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.52,0:22:32.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Smiley?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.13,0:23:27.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ultimate weapon that Caesar created...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.41,0:23:30.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,While its identity is slowly coming to light,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.74,0:23:34.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Straw Hats make their move to capture Caesar.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.49,0:23:40.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, Luffy's actions cause the \Nsituation to go in an unexpected direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.06,0:23:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.40,0:23:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Capture M! \NThe Pirate Alliance's Operation Launches!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.80,0:23:46.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.98,0:23:48.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
